{"type": "article", "id": 13547, "title": "就算生活有千百种难过，下个单就好？", "description": "买买买有一千种理由，不变的核心是治愈。", "date": "2015-08-15T07:20:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8721, "name": "Prime"}, {"id": 85, "name": "亚马逊"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144609Qa2c6X8zC7oR1eOW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>一只瘸了腿的小狗，天可怜见的。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>不能像别的狗狗一样追逐皮球、飞快地掠过草坪、蹦跶在大步流星的主人左右。他的主人也忧郁地凝视着他，凝视着他……直到拿出手机在亚马逊上下了个单，马上一切都变得不一样了呢</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/html5embed.action?type=0&amp;code=gV3IIb_xEak&amp;lcode=&amp;resourceId=380561142_06_05_99\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是亚马逊为其会员服务 </span><span>Prime </span><span>推出的最新广告，去年</span><span> 3 </span><span>月份，亚马逊将会费从 </span><span>79 </span><span>美元上涨到 </span><span>99 </span><span>美元，这还是九年来的头一次。（注：</span><span>Prime</span><span> 用户可以享受免运费两天送达，在线观影及 </span><span>Kindle</span><span> 图书馆的部分免费资源）</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>亚马逊不太担心会因为涨价而流失客户，因为还没出现直接竞争者与亚马逊的会员配送服务争夺客户资源。而在 </span><span>Kindle</span><span> 和亚马逊网络服务上提价是比较困难的，亚马逊不得不维持与微软和</span><span> Rackspace’s</span><span> 相似的价位。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>即使如此，亚马逊还是毫不掉以轻心地祭出萌宠和小</span><span> Baby</span><span> 来感化你。唯一的问题是，第二个广告里的小男孩儿怎么看都是穿哈利波特的巫师服更合适一些。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>下单，别犹豫。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/html5embed.action?type=0&amp;code=Zx_XtPom6F0&amp;lcode=&amp;resourceId=380561142_06_05_99\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}